[It would not be surprising if chikungunya virus appears in other Pacific islands, or from islands where the virus is being transmitted currently to the mainland in the Americas. ProMED will appreciate receiving additional reports from New Caledonia if further cases appear there.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of New Caledonia can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/4wEV. - Mod.TY]
